le, Flucytosine, Tioconazole, Tetracycline, Minocycline, Doxycycline, More', 'Chlorpromazine, Mesoridazine, Methotrimeprazine, Promazine, Fluphenazine, Asenapine, Perphenazine, Thiothixene, Thioridazine, Trifluoperazine, Amisulpride, More', 1767369485);
